<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,403,151,178]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Rohrthrips breviceps</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Ulitzka, M. R." box="[410,575,151,177]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="27 - 40" refId="ref30168" refString="Ulitzka, M. R. (2019) Five new species of Rohrthrips (Thysanoptera: Rohrthripidae) from Burmese amber, and the evolution of Tubulifera wings. Zootaxa, 4585 (1), 27 - 40. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4585.1.2" type="journal article" year="2019">Ulitzka, 2019</bibRefCitation>
